主题: <strong>特殊的投掷武器</strong><br>
作者: <strong>折剑者绯月</strong> 于 <strong>2017-03-23, 周四 21:35:51</strong>
<dd class="postbody">
<span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size"><strong>特殊的投掷武器</strong></span><br>这些投掷武器被当做了弹药。<br><table class="bbc_table"><tr><td><strong>物品名称</strong><td><strong>价格</strong>　　<td><strong>伤害（S）</strong><td><strong>伤害（M）</strong><td><strong>重击</strong>　<td><strong>射程</strong>　<td><strong>重量</strong>　<td><strong>类型</strong>　<td><strong>特性</strong>　<td><strong>出处</strong></tr><tr><td>飞镖<td>5SP<td>1D3<td>1D4<td>X2<td>20尺<td>0.5磅<td>穿刺<td>-<td>CRB</tr><tr><td>手里剑（5）<td>1GP<td>1<td>1D2<td>X2<td>10尺<td>0.5磅<td>穿刺<td>武僧<td>CRB</tr><tr><td>羽量飞镖（10）<td>1GP<td>-<td>-<td>-<td>-<td>-<td>-<td>见下文<td>UI</tr><tr><td>震电飞镖<td>100GP<td>1D3<td>1D4<td>X2<td>20尺<td>0.5磅<td>穿刺<td>见下文<td>ARG</tr></table><hr /><strong>飞镖 Dart</strong><br>这件具有配重的投掷武器比箭矢大，尺寸和射程则较标枪为短。多数飞镖为木柄铁尖<br><br><strong>手里剑 Shuriken</strong><br>手里剑是一小片边缘锋利、被设计用来投掷的金属片。手里剑无法被当作近战武器使用。虽然是投掷武器，手里剑在决定精制品等特殊版本的制造与价格、以及投出后的效果时视为弹药。<br><br><strong>羽量飞镖 Featherweight Dart</strong><br>这些极为轻巧的飞镖如同吹箭，除了它们被用于悄悄地传递毒素而不是造成伤害。当你以此飞镖命中一个敌人，毒素会在飞镖脱落时注入目标体内，并且令伤口难以愈合。任何伤害减免，硬度或者类似防护可以阻止飞镖传递毒素。任何对目标的检查必须通过DC20的察觉检定来发现被飞镖穿刺的伤口，以及寻找飞镖掉落的地方需要DC15的察觉检定。这种弹药可以用于吹箭或手腕发射器。<br><div>These extremely small and lightweight darts function like blowgun darts, except they are used to deliver poisons surreptitiously instead of dealing damage. When you hit with a dart, the poison is injected into the target while the dart breaks off and falls away, leaving the wound hard to spot. Any amount of damage reduction, hardness, or similar protection prevents the featherweight dart from delivering its injected poison. Anyone examining the target must succeed at a DC 20 Perception check to find the puncture wound, while finding the dart itself at the location where it fell requires a successful DC 15 Perception check. This ammunition can be used in both blowguns and wrist launchers.</div><strong>震电飞镖 Jolting Dart</strong><br>这种通过炼金术种植的晶体飞镖在投掷出去之后会产生电荷。被飞镖击中的目标会受到正常穿刺伤害以及1d6点闪电伤害。任何擅长使用飞镖的人都可以使用震击飞镖。飞镖一旦掷出就会损毁。<br><div>Jolting Dart: This alchemically grown crystal dart builds up an electrical charge when thrown. A creature struck by the dart takes normal piercing damage and 1d6 points of electricity damage. Anyone proficient in darts can use a jolting dart. Once thrown, the dart is destroyed.<br></div><br>
